FBIS3-37282 "drsov032_c_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 Federal Assembly Duma Approves Draft Law on Media Coverage LD1502202194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1630 GMT 15 Feb 94 LD1502202194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] At a sitting of Russia's State Duma today, the Committee for Information Policy and Communications approved a draft law on media coverage of State Duma proceedings. It has been proposed that a special press service be set up to prepare television and radio programs using the equipment and studios of Russian TV Parliament.
